title: Chinese Ceramics From Japanese Collections - T'ang Through Ming
description:
Chinese Ceramics From Japanese Collections - T'ang Through Ming Dynasties
Asia House Gallery | 1977 | ISBN 0878480498 | English | 144 pages | PDF | 14.5 MB

An exhibition of Chinese ceramics from public and private collections in Japan organized under the joint sponsorship of the Agency for Cultural Affairs of the Japanese Government and the participating institutions in the United States
